        <h1>Stranger Things</h1>
        <p>
            Set in the 1980s in the fictional town of Hawkins, Indiana, Stranger Things follows a group of young friends
            who uncover supernatural events and secret government experiments while trying to find their missing friend, Will Byers.
            The series blends sci-fi, horror, and nostalgic pop culture references.
        </p>
